Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:38.77,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我对运气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:44.03,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}无所指望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:48.68,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:52.66,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.85,0:23:56.20,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}有所准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:03.19,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我将自行斩断退路
